<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#707070">[فِي الوَقْفِ عَلَى أَوَاخِرِ الكَلِمِ]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٠٤ - وَحَاذِرِ الوَقْفَ بِكُلِّ الحَرَكَهْ … إِلَّا إِذَا رُمْتَ فَبَعْضُ الحَرَكَهْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١٠٥ - إِلَّا بِفَتْحٍ أَوْ بِنَصْبٍ،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَأَشِمْ … إِشَارَةً بِالضَّمِّ:</span> فِي رَفْعٍ وَضَمْ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>* * *<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>